						<summary>

						<p>This records an agreement given by the temple servants <hi rend="italic">(patipādamūlattār)</hi> to burn a perpetual lamp in the temple, for 25 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of pure tested gold received by them from Śēkkiḻāṉ Sattimalaiyaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Śōḻamuttaraiyaṉ of Kāvanur in Mēlūr-kōṭṭam.</p>						

						</summary>
